org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.model.api

Interface Rule

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RuleImpl

    public interface Rule
    Interface for classes representing a rule. This implementation assumes that rules are defined by their head and body literals, without explicitly specifying quantifiers. All variables in the body are considered universally quantified; all variables in the head that do not occur in the body are considered existentially quantified.
